To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private UltimateOscillator _ultosc;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ultosc = ULTOSC(symbol, period1, period2, period3);

// In OnData()
if (_ultosc.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "ultimateoscillator", _ultosc.Current.Value);
}
